title: 2Pac 4 Life Collection (M3 Software - a.k.a. 3ogdy)
description:
This is a 2Pac Collection (songs only). Actually it's made by every single 2Pac song I have in my PC.
Some songs were extracted from videos. There are various 320kbit songs.
There are both remixes and originals.
There are various songs with the same name - it's because one of them is BASS-optimized.
There are some remixes of Pac's songs that I thought were worth including in this collection.
As a fan of 2Pac I would suggest checking some T-Bizzy songs too (Never Change and some others) as the king of Rap/Hip-Hop is T-Bizzy's inspiration.

Enjoy this collection and please seed.
